00:23:48.920 --> 00:23:52.390 align:middle line:84%
So what we have
to do is actually

00:23:52.390 --> 00:23:56.340 align:middle line:84%
discover the inner
source of the breath.

00:23:56.340 --> 00:24:01.300 align:middle line:10%
And if you follow your breath,
what you will start to notice

00:24:01.300 --> 00:24:05.680 align:middle line:10%
is that the diaphragm,
this muscle that

00:24:05.680 --> 00:24:08.020 align:middle line:10%
runs across the bottom
of your rib cage,

00:24:08.020 --> 00:24:11.270 align:middle line:10%
is actually rising and
falling with the breath.

00:24:11.270 --> 00:24:13.480 align:middle line:84%
And if you allow
yourself to tune

00:24:13.480 --> 00:24:15.800 align:middle line:84%
into the diaphragm
as your breathing,

00:24:15.800 --> 00:24:18.250 align:middle line:84%
you begin to
recognize that breath

00:24:18.250 --> 00:24:20.590 align:middle line:90%
starts from inside the body.

00:24:20.590 --> 00:24:22.240 align:middle line:10%
We think that
breath is something

00:24:22.240 --> 00:24:24.640 align:middle line:10%
you take in from outside
through your nostrils.

00:24:24.640 --> 00:24:27.880 align:middle line:10%
In fact, the gesture of
breathing starts inside.

00:24:27.880 --> 00:24:32.110 align:middle line:10%
And if you're focused here in
this region, between the heart

00:24:32.110 --> 00:24:35.380 align:middle line:10%
and the solar plexus,
and allowing the breath

00:24:35.380 --> 00:24:40.690 align:middle line:10%
to come in while your
focus remains there,

00:24:40.690 --> 00:24:43.970 align:middle line:10%
something opens up
in your inner body.

00:24:43.970 --> 00:24:48.640 align:middle line:10%
And you start to recognize that
there's a wisdom and a power

00:24:48.640 --> 00:24:50.830 align:middle line:10%
that you're carrying
inside you that

00:24:50.830 --> 00:24:52.990 align:middle line:10%
is deeper than the
mind, which is literally

00:24:52.990 --> 00:24:56.170 align:middle line:10%
the source of your breath,
which is your own life force.

00:24:56.170 --> 00:24:58.840 align:middle line:10%
And that's where true power is.

00:24:58.840 --> 00:25:00.940 align:middle line:10%
That power is fearless.

00:25:00.940 --> 00:25:03.460 align:middle line:84%
In other words,
