00:25:03.460 --> 00:25:07.460 align:middle line:84%
in the middle of the most
challenging external situation.

00:25:07.460 --> 00:25:10.240 align:middle line:84%
And it's all about
learning to find

00:25:10.240 --> 00:25:14.200 align:middle line:84%
the source of your own breath,
which we do by literally

00:25:14.200 --> 00:25:18.680 align:middle line:84%
following the breath, until
we can discern the place where

00:25:18.680 --> 00:25:20.570 align:middle line:90%
the breath starts.

00:25:20.570 --> 00:25:24.410 align:middle line:84%
And then letting it rise,
fill our lungs, go out,

00:25:24.410 --> 00:25:27.500 align:middle line:84%
do what it does,
and then coming back

00:25:27.500 --> 00:25:30.590 align:middle line:84%
to that place which is the
source of the inhalation.

00:25:30.590 --> 00:25:36.440 align:middle line:84%
It will, over time, change your
whole relationship to yourself.

00:25:36.440 --> 00:25:39.170 align:middle line:84%
And then when you
act, when you speak,

00:25:39.170 --> 00:25:42.230 align:middle line:84%
when you interact
with others, it

00:25:42.230 --> 00:25:45.480 align:middle line:84%
will be from a place
of interior connection.

00:25:45.480 --> 00:25:49.790 align:middle line:10%
And you'll be able to find
that same interior connection

00:25:49.790 --> 00:25:52.010 align:middle line:10%
in other people.

00:25:52.010 --> 00:25:53.780 align:middle line:10%
And it's at that
point that we start

00:25:53.780 --> 00:25:56.120 align:middle line:10%
to realize what
human equality really

00:25:56.120 --> 00:26:01.460 align:middle line:10%
